Available Commands:

Basic Commands:
  help      - Display help topics
  look      - Look at your surroundings
  say       - Say something to others
  quit      - Exit the game
  who       - See who is online

Communication:
  say <message>    - Say something aloud
  tell <user> <msg> - Send a private message

Information:
  look             - Look around
  inventory        - Check your inventory
  score            - View your character stats

For detailed help on any command, type:
  help <command>
